              <history-note id="DLM1019639"><amended-provision>Section 75(2A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM410638">section 38(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Sentencing Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 27).</history-note>
              <history-note id="DLM1019640"><amended-provision>Section 75(3)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM410638">section 38(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Sentencing Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 27).</history-note>
