                  <para>
                    <text><def-term id="DLM3023004">record of final warning</def-term>, in relation to an offender, means a record of a warning that the offender has under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM3023016">section 86C(3)</intref></citation> or <citation jurisdiction="nz"/><citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM3023018">86E(8)</intref></citation></text>
                  </para>
                </def-para>
                <def-para id="DLM3023005">
                  <para>
                    <text><def-term id="DLM3023006">record of first warning</def-term>, in relation to an offender, means a record of a warning that the offender has under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM3023015">section 86B(3)</intref></citation></text>
